net.sf.jclec.syntaxtree

Class NonTerminalNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jclec.syntaxtree.SyntaxTreeNode
      • net.sf.jclec.syntaxtree.NonTerminalNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, JCLEC

    public class NonTerminalNode
extends SyntaxTreeNode
    Non terminal node (containing a non-terminal symbol) in a syntax tree. Non terminal nodes contain a reference to a String [], representing the production rule that is being applying.
    Author:
    Sebastian Ventura
